Sunburn is a 1979 British-American comedy film directed by Richard C. Sarafian and written by James Booth , John Daly and Stephen Oliver .
It is based on the novel The Bind by Stanley Ellin .
The film stars Farrah Fawcett , Charles Grodin , Art Carney , Joan Collins , William Daniels and John Hillerman .
The film was released on August 10 , 1979 , by Paramount Pictures .